    <panel_attributes>BasicAuthenticator如何执行认证逻辑呢?
调用BasicAuthenticator.authenticate()方法认证
authenticate()方法就是从servlet请求header中解析出
authorization字段,并且从authorization中解析出
username/password
style=wordwrap</panel_attributes>
